title: Tito & Tarantula - Tarantism (1997) [FLAC]
description:
the band 'From Dusk Till Dawn' performing at the 'Titty Twister' club

their debut album includes two songs from the 'from Dusk Till Dawn' soundtrack ("Angry Cockroaches", "After Dark") and two from the 'Desperado' soundtrack ("Strange Face of Love", "Back to the House that Love Built") plus six new songs
